					p Little Benchmark provides SoC and IC benchmarking, testing, inspection, auditing, advising and training services to a wide range of clients, including manufacturers, retailers, policymakers, regulators, service companies, and consumers.
					br
					p Our customers have niche and complex requirements and are predominantly found in the microprocessor, FPGA and integrated circuit manufacturing markets. Founded in 2016, our goals are to abandon the traditional path of collecting intellectual property and instead approach our testing and manufacturing goals in an open source and globally collaborative manner. We provide a foundation of testing tools and borrow the brain power of the masses to complete the hardest problems. This is all made possible due to the prosperity of the open hardware and source code movements. Little Benchmark customers rely on our community, unique expertise, ferocious desire to stress test even the most extreme data processing topologies and research. This validation and high quality and high performance service is the only thing that allows them to most effectively deliver their products and get to market faster than their competitors.

				
		
